            <title>[CASSANDRA-911] QuorumResponseHandler sets timeout incorrectly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-911</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We noticed that the timeout calculation seems wrong:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;long timeout = System.currentTimeMillis() - startTime + DatabaseDescriptor.getRpcTimeout();&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Lets propose that 3 seconds elapse (currentTime - startTime). It will take that value and add the default RpcTimeout (5 seconds) making the timeout 8 seconds.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
